a("Battle of Myeongnyang","1597-10-26","1597-10-26","Korea",["Battle","Naval Battle"],"The Battle of Myeongnyang in 1597 was one of history's most remarkable naval victories. Admiral Yi Sun-sin with only 13 ships defeated 133 Japanese warships by exploiting the narrow strait's currents.",[["1597","Second Japanese invasion"],["1597","Yi Sun-sin reinstated"],["1597-10-26","Japanese enter strait"],["1597-10-26","Strong currents trap ships"],["1597-10-26","13 defeat 133 warships"],["1597","31 Japanese ships destroyed"]]);
